author: veithen
msg: Use maven-shade-plugin to produce the sandesha2-client-constants JAR. This has the advantage that the resulting Maven artifact no longer has a dependency on sandesha2-core (from which sandesha2-client-constants is extracted). This is because maven-shade-plugin produces a dependency reduced JAR.
